The paper deals with security in cyber physical systems, specifically in the context of feedback control systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses attacks on sensors and actuators, which falls under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves multirate sampled data controllers, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the use of controllers to detect attacks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
